    "content": "<div class=\"noinclude\">\n <span class=\"breadcrumbs XULRefProp_breadcrumbs\">« <a href=\"/en-US/docs/XUL_Reference\" title=\"XUL_Reference\">XUL Reference</a></span></div>\n<dl>\n <dt>\n  <code><span><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/XUL/Property/maxWidth\">maxWidth</a></span></code></dt>\n <dd>\n  Type: <em>integer</em></dd>\n <dd>\n  Gets and sets the value of the <code id=\"a-maxwidth\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/maxwidth\">maxwidth</a></code> attribute.</dd>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"noinclude\">\n <div class=\"note\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> Prior to <span title=\"(Firefox 6.0 / Thunderbird 6.0 / SeaMonkey 2.3)\">Gecko 6.0</span>, you could use this on <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\" title=\"The HTML &lt;input> element is used to create interactive controls for web-based forms in order to accept data from the user; a wide variety of types of input data and control widgets are available, depending on the device and user agent.\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> elements; this was never intended, was a violation of the HTML specification, and has been fixed. Use the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input#attr-size\">size</a></code> to set the maximum width of input fields.</p>\n </div>\n</div>\n<p> </p>",
    "contributors": "<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/wbamberg\">wbamberg</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/mdnwebdocs-bot\">mdnwebdocs-bot</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/Sheppy\">Sheppy</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/kscarfone\">kscarfone</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/trevorh\">trevorh</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/karindpowell@yahoo.com\">karindpowell@yahoo.com</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/Marsf\">Marsf</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/BenoitL\">BenoitL</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/Mgjbot\">Mgjbot</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/Ptak82\">Ptak82</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/Dria\">Dria</a>",
    "title": "maxWidth"
